### Rebuild
1. Delete these folders:
   - `/.mono`
   - `/Tests/bin`
   - `/Tests/obj`
2. Click on rebuild from Godot_mono. Godot will create them again.

### Organization

- Scripts should be placed in the `/Game` folder.
- All scripts attached to any Godot game object should be place in the `/Game/Controller` folder.
It means if you rename or move any of these 'controller' scripts, you have to update your scenes.
